item.title: ABSTRACT: The Narrator and the Noise
item.description: Preface This blog post is simply the summary of The Narrator and the Noise. Please read the full version at either of the following locations: Gitbook version: https://rs-ddlc.netlify.com/ PDF version: https://github.com/robertschnitman/RS_Reports/blob/master/DDLC/DDLC.pdf Abstract The focus of this study is to determine the existence and extent of statistical bias towards any of the Doki Doki Literature Club characters with respect to the points distribution of the Poem Minigame.
